  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Holidays to Italy from Newcastle International Airport</h2>
<p>Looking for Italy holidays from Newcastle? Get ready to experience the beauty of stunning landscapes, hidden historical gems, and the relaxed dolce vita lifestyle. We’ve got you covered from flights to hotel and transfers, so you can sit back, relax, and let us take care of all the details.</p>
<p><img style="width: 853px; height: 457px;" src="/media/13097453/portofino-1.jpg?width=853&amp;height=457&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/23bf40c025754b459500204bf0676173" /></p>
<p>Our Italy holidays are a cocktail of cultural wonders, scenic shorelines and historic sights - like a perfect Italian Spritz. From sipping espresso in charming Italian cafes, to wandering through vibrant piazzas and indulging in tasty Gelato, Italy is simply bursting with flavours.</p>
<p>And for those seeking some R&amp;R, the Italian lakes offer a serene escape with their scenic views, sparkling waters and laid back towns. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1c42e2d17ecd4d14b5ec23a3a62b7917" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1c42e2d17ecd4d14b5ec23a3a62b7917}" title="From Newcastle" class="c-btn">View holidays from Newcastle</a></p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Italy Holiday Destinations from Newcastle</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/759f24b262fb4f3fbdbb264c2fb4f67b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/759f24b262fb4f3fbdbb264c2fb4f67b}#Lake" title="Italy Holidays from Newcastle" data-anchor="#Lake">Lake Holidays</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/759f24b262fb4f3fbdbb264c2fb4f67b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/759f24b262fb4f3fbdbb264c2fb4f67b}#Mountain" title="Italy Holidays from Newcastle" data-anchor="#Mountain">Mountain Holidays</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/759f24b262fb4f3fbdbb264c2fb4f67b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/759f24b262fb4f3fbdbb264c2fb4f67b}#City" title="Italy Holidays from Newcastle" data-anchor="#City">City Break</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 841px; height: 451px;" src="/media/13097451/walking-holidays-1.jpg?width=841&amp;height=451&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2b1678412ddb4337a01a3ab6f2688d90" /></p>
<div>Prepare to be charmed by Italy’s magnificent resorts, where the dolce vita is the secret ingredient that makes every moment ‘bellissimo.’</div>
<div></div>
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Lake"></a></p>
<h3>Italy Lake Holidays from Newcastle Airport</h3>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo">Lake Iseo Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 270px;" src="/media/13097471/lake-iseo_adobestock_378117848.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/d10cab9129c84824a510824e94c27926" /></p>
<p>Uncover the hidden gem of Lake Iseo, a lesser-known lake tucked away in Lombardy, Northern Italy. From winding medieval streets to charming family-run vineyards, there is an abundance of things to see and do in the area.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo" class="c-btn">View Lake Iseo Holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b}" title="Lake Ledro">Lake Ledro Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 270px;" src="/media/13097472/lake-ledro-italy-2.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/0043bd0dc8894881a3b01b45c9de74a2" /></p>
<p>Located north of Lake Garda and standing nearly 600 meters higher, this breath-taking alpine lake is a hidden gem. With its mesmerizing turquoise blue waters, it provides the ideal setting for a tranquil walking holiday.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b}" title="Lake Ledro" class="c-btn">View Lake Ledro Holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 270px;" src="/media/13097475/limone-sul-garda-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/37a54c86726c4f30a14043bcd4153d77" /></p>
<p>Lake Garda is the largest lake in Italy. The southern part is dotted with popular resorts, perfect for wine tasting and city sightseeing. Whilst the northern region is a haven for an active holiday, providing opportunities for walking, cycling, and water sports.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda" class="c-btn">View Lake Garda Holidays</a></div>
</div>
