<p><a name="Mountain"></a></p>
<h3>Italy Mountain Holidays from Newcastle Airport</h3>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 270px;" src="/media/13097569/puez-odle-selva.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/751b95cec3b24faebb1f90665b81eb50" /></p>
<p>Selva is a village in the famous Val Gardena in the <a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites">Dolomites.</a> The entire area is a network of national parks, nature reserves, and conservation areas, providing a haven for nature lovers.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva" class="c-btn">View Selva Holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082}" title="Canazei">Canazei Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 270px;" src="/media/13097570/016-ralf-brunel-1154-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a2a6de54914346f499f0642b7395b001" /></p>
<p>Canazei boasts a breath-taking location, surrounded by the magnificent mountains of the Dolomites. Marvel at the stunning views from the top of Marmolada or challenge yourself by ascending the well-maintained paths leading to the summit of Piz Boe.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082}" title="Canazei" class="c-btn">View Canazei Holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/a7a8ad5233804c39b1e02e8dd02cc1fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a7a8ad5233804c39b1e02e8dd02cc1fc}" title="Ortisei">Ortisei Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 270px;" src="/media/13097571/14174740871_aea47b3ce9_o-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/62634691fad34213abb3d6cd669c0d5f" /></p>
<p>This authentic mountain village offers a pedestrianized centre bustling with local shops and charming family-run restaurants, perfect for grabbing a delicious meal. Plus, with all the activities of the Dolomites right at your doorstep, you'll have endless excitement and adventure awaiting you.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/a7a8ad5233804c39b1e02e8dd02cc1fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a7a8ad5233804c39b1e02e8dd02cc1fc}" title="Ortisei" class="c-btn">View Ortisei Holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 270px;" src="/media/13097573/merano-italy-cover.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/577c149dcb8145bb8416b20837508f5c" /></p>
<p>Merano, a spa town in a vineyard-filled valley, is rich in culture and history. With walking trails in every direction, it's a perfect destination for exploration. Enjoy the rejuvenating radon springs and medieval charm of this South Tyrolean gem.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano" class="c-btn">View Merano Holidays</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p><a name="City"></a></p>
<h3>Italy City Break from Newcastle</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b}" title="Verona">Verona Holidays</a></h4>
<p><img style="width: 866px; height: 464px;" src="/media/13097575/verona-italy.jpg?width=866&amp;height=464&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f9c837bbf1624d69b105081d047bb73d" /></p>
<p>Uncover Italy's art, history, and culinary delights during a city break. Verona, renowned as the city of Romeo and Juliet, offers a captivating history that predates Shakespeare's iconic tale. Discover the rich heritage of this enchanting city, where ancient roots intertwine with timeless romance.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b}" title="Verona" class="c-btn">View Verona Holidays</a></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
